org.safs.auth

Class AuthorizationServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.persist.PersistableDefault
      • org.safs.auth.AuthorizationServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Persistable, Printable

    public class AuthorizationServer
extends PersistableDefault
    This class encapsulates the information about the authorization server, where client/application/consumer can get the 'authorization code', 'access token', 'refresh token' etc.
    Author:
    Lei Wang
